properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper in back').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth + thisLayer.effect('Bell End')('Outline Width') * 2

properties.name: Size
properties.expression: const temp = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower in front').content('Stroke').strokeWidth;[temp, temp]

properties.name: Start
properties.expression: function getPathLength ( pathToMeasure = thisProperty, samplePts = 20 ) {		const getLayerFromProp = prop => {		let parentItem = prop.propertyGroup( 1 );		while ( !( parentItem instanceof Layer ) ) {			parentItem = parentItem.propertyGroup( 1 );		}		return parentItem;	};	const divisor = ( 1 / ( samplePts - 1 ) );	const pointArray = [ ...Array( samplePts ) ].map( ( p, i ) => {			return pathToMeasure.pointOnPath( i * divisor );	} );	const getSegLength = ( acc, curr, i, arr ) => {		return acc + thisLayer.length( curr, arr[ i + 1 ] || curr )	};	return pointArray.reduce( getSegLength, 0 );}const pathLength = getPathLength(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower in front').content('Path').path);const ellipseRadius = (thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Rim').content('Sleeve End Group').transform.scale[1] * thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Rim').content('Sleeve End Group').content('Ellipse Path').size[1] * 0.01) - thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Rim').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth - thisLayer.effect('Bell End')('Outline Width');thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper in back').content('Trim Paths').end - (ellipseRadius / pathLength * 50)

properties.name: Size
properties.expression: const temp = 100 + thisLayer.effect('Bell End')('Opening Offset') ;[temp, temp]

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const mywidth = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper in back').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth;const rounding = thisLayer.effect('Bell End')('Rounding');const yScale = rounding == 0 ? 0.1 : rounding * 0.01 * mywidth;[mywidth,  yScale]

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function strokePath() {        // Limber Stroke        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.scale[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p3ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.anchorPoint.value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.position.value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p3ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos, [0, 0]], [[0, 0], thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }strokePath();// Limber Library strokePath
